trans-unit.source: The TPM OM API reference lists the different entities and their properties that are exposed by the TPM object model.

trans-unit.source: The <codeInline>TpmContext</codeInline> is the base entity and the starting point for all operations related to TPM OM API.
trans-unit.target: The <codeInline>TpmContext</codeInline> is the base entity and the starting point for all operations related to TPM OM API.
